{"Body":"<p>I have seen two versions:</p>\n\n<p>a) *<em>-ia</em> ending actually derived from the collective number form, which also ends in *<em>-ia</em>. So the collective number first started to represent abstract things (compare Latin <em>animalia</em>, Greek <em>zooia</em>), and then came to mark feminine gender.</p>\n\n<p>b) From Eurasiatic *<em>haia</em>, \"mother\", from Borean *<em>haia</em>, \"mother\" (see <a href=\"http://starling.rinet.ru/cgi-bin/response.cgi?root=config&amp;morpho=0&amp;basename=%5Cdata%5Cnostr%5Cnostret&amp;first=1&amp;off=&amp;text_proto=%CA%94VjV&amp;method_proto=substring&amp;ic_proto=on&amp;text_meaning=mother&amp;method_meaning=substring&amp;ic_meaning=on&amp;text_ier=&amp;method_ier=substring&amp;ic_ier=on&amp;text_alt=&amp;method_alt=substring&amp;ic_alt=on&amp;text_ura=&amp;method_ura=substring&amp;ic_ura=on&amp;text_kart=&amp;method_kart=substring&amp;ic_kart=on&amp;text_drav=&amp;method_drav=substring&amp;ic_drav=on&amp;text_esk=&amp;method_esk=substring&amp;ic_esk=on&amp;text_chuk=&amp;method_chuk=substring&amp;ic_chuk=on&amp;text_notes=&amp;method_notes=substring&amp;ic_notes=on&amp;text_reference=&amp;method_reference=substring&amp;ic_reference=on&amp;text_any=&amp;method_any=substring&amp;sort=proto&amp;ic_any=on\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nostratic etymology</a>) which explains similar feminine *<em>-ia</em> endings in Semitic, IE and Altaic.</p>\n\n<p>The account for Laryngeal theory is only compatible with version a) and cannot explain how Eurasiatic *<em>-ia</em> became PIE *<em>-ih<sub>2</sub>.</em></p>\n", "Id":"1258", "LastEditorUserId":"624", "Title":"What is the origin of feminine ending *-ia in PIE?", "CreationDate":"2012-01-11T03:20:16.850", "OwnerUserId":"624", "PostTypeId":"1", "Tags":"<gender><proto-indo-european>", "AnswerCount":"1", "comments":[], "LastEditDate":"2012-01-12T06:20:35.017", "LastEditedUser":{"UpVotes":"81", "DownVotes":"60", "Id":"624", "AccountId":"407237", "Views":"34", "Reputation":"1743", "CreationDate":"2011-12-28T07:24:31.420", "DisplayName":"Anixx", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-18T10:33:34.597"}, "ViewCount":"224", "LastActivityDate":"2012-10-11T04:48:14.977", "Score":"5", "CommentCount":"4", "OwnerUser":{"UpVotes":"81", "DownVotes":"60", "Id":"624", "AccountId":"407237", "Views":"34", "Reputation":"1743", "CreationDate":"2011-12-28T07:24:31.420", "DisplayName":"Anixx", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-18T10:33:34.597"}}